<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90cbcbc8-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s6915"><num value="6915">§ 6915.</num><heading> Expenditure of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For each fiscal year for which an appropriation is made to the Commission, the Commission shall issue a report to the Congress on its expenditures under that appropriation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90cbcbc9-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/286/dB/tIII/s305">Pub. L. 106–286, div. B, title III, § 305</ref>, <date date="2000-10-10">Oct. 10, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/899">114 Stat. 899</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
